storyInfo: Lava realizes Hibiscus is sick, and after caring for her sister, takes a moment to close her eyes and rest. When she wakes up, she finds out all of a sudden it was just a dream, and she's the one who's actually ill.

attributes.content: Tick—tick—tick—tick—
Tick—tick—tick—tick—
Tick—tick—tick—tick—
Bang.
Augh... shut up...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hibiscus, time to get up.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: You're not even gonna answer?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: No way you're thinking of lying in.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: You sent me a message yesterday saying you were making rounds or something. That I should wake you up in the morning.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And here I am awake, and you're still sleeping. Haaah...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Eh, sleep in all you want. I'm gonna go rinse up.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hibiscus, you're still sleeping?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Wanna get up?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I just got back from field work myself. The mission wasn't easy. A huge hassle, actually. Not many people other than me could deal with it.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And Amiya gave me a hell of a lot of off days for it, so now I can sleep in for the whole day.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: If I wasn't getting you up, I could've gotten a lot more sleep. Haaah...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Still asleep?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Then I've got to do something or other.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: You said yourself last night, you were one of the Medical Department's elite at this point. You can't be late. I'll drag you out if I have to.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Though saying that isn't a first for me...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: But having the chance to actually drag you out from your covers would be.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hm-hmmm. What in the world would you do without me?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Still not getting up? I'm seriously gonna pull 'em. If you catch a cold, don't blame me.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hibi—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hibiscus, what—what's up with you?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Why are your hands so hot?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hibiscus? Sis? Don't kid me like this. Haven't you always been pretty healthy?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Why would you just...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Sis! Sis! Say something!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I'm awake... Lava...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Stop shaking me...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Oh, s—sorry.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Are you okay?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: A little chilly... and weak...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Probably caught a fever...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Fever? Your body can do that?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh, right!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Just wait for me a moment, I'll go and find a doctor for you right now!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It's no big deal... Lava, you don't need to...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Oh... honestly, you...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Ten minutes later...
Hibiscus, I found a doctor for you!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ansel, you need to take a look quick! Is she alright?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Wait, calm down—ack, stop pulling me like that—
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Good grief... I thought you had something urgent you needed to drag me out for. I see it was your sister.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: It's n... nothing...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: The sick aren't qualified to say it's 'nothing.'
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Hmm...
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Do you have a thermometer in your dormitory?
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: We—We do!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: In our household medicine box...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I'll go and get it!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Don't rush.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: It's just... a fever...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Hrmm.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Temperature's a little high.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: And you're unable to exert strength?
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Mm-hm...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Medicine box! Come on! I remember it was here!
Have your diet and work-rest balance been fine these past few days?
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Health...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Healthy meals.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Okay, forget I ever asked.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: You and Folinic are both the type that don't call for worrying.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: You've likely been too exhausted as of recent.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Found it!
Do the necessary... tests too... in a bit, please...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: That way she can... feel a little calmer...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I understand.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Here, the thermometer!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Please bring the whole chest over. I can administer Hibiscus all the fundamental tests that way.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: A medical kit of hers should contain the necessary equipment.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Got it!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: With sufficient supporting data, I'll be able to discern whether her high temperature is a protective bodily response, or whether some other symptom has had knock-on complications.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: We'll start with temperature. Here, open wide.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Aaah—
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: H—How is she?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: No great cause for worry. Her body is just self-regulating somewhat aggressively.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Overexhaustion should be the main cause.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: As long as she rests up for the next few days, she'll be back again in no time.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: She'll want a bit of a lighter diet, reduced salt and sugar intake, and to pay mind to balanced nutrition.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: So you're saying I've gotta make healthy meals for her...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: The cafeteria can provide similar meals. You might not necessarily have to make them yourself.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: As for other major points, Hibiscus knows more than well enough, so I won't go listing.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: I'll file Hibiscus' sick leave for her at the Medical Department. Fang will tell the others.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: The both of you shouldn't have any field work or missions lined up for the next couple of days, correct.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: I don't, no.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: None...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Then there shouldn't be any problem.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: If you don't have any particular questions, then I'll be on my way. I'll leave you to watch over her, Lava.
attributes.name: Ansel

attributes.content: Hey—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: So I gotta look after you for a day or two, then.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ah...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I never took any sort of nursing class.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Lava... if you want to train... go train...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Your sister's... a doctor... she's not that weak...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: She can look after... herself...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: *Cough*, *cough* *cough*...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: That's enough out of you! Does your throat hurt? Do you need some water?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It's okay...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Look, I, uh, I wasn't—I'm not saying I don't wanna look after you!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It's just, that, I, I don't really have experience...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: So if I get any part wrong. If you're uncomfortable.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Then tell me.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Lava...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Okay...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Then we're doing this. You need to eat breakfast first. I'll go make some in a moment. I'll do the dishes after we're done.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Is your appetite gonna be a problem?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It won't...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Hmm...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Want me to get a washbowl first, then, so you can wash your face and stuff?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Nods)
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Just give me a moment.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Pulls at a corner of Lava's hem)
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Oh. Is there anything else?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Mouths a 'thank you')
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Nothing to thank me for. You got ill. I'm off for a couple days. It pretty much works out.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Uh, where'd that washbowl from before go?
Phew... finally, all done...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Jeez, nursing's rougher than I thought. I don't feel cool at all.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: If you asked me to do this in front of everyone else, I'd refuse point blank.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Are you full?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Nods)
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Then you can go back to sleep now.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Close your eyes, and get some proper rest.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I'll wash out the bowl, and then I'll go do the dishes, and then—not sure.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Eh, anyhow, for now that's that. If you need anything, set the alarm on this clock to go off. I'll come right over when I hear it.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Be good.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Pats Hibiscus's face)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Mmnn... brush, washing-up liquid.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Did I give Hibiscus's face a pat just then?)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Mum and dad'll miss you.
Don't forget to write to us.
Be good.
Hmph...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Mum and dad love treating us like that.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Not sure if they've gotten the letter from last week yet.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Mm... is that how Hibiscus treats me too?)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: You need to eat healthy meals.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Be good.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (Whenever she acts like that, chances are she's trying to boss me around.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (I don't know if that one bowl of meat porridge was enough to fill her.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Should I peel her a piece of fruit too?)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Or maybe roast some meat?)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (I really wanna set up a stove right by her bed and barbecue meat for myself.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Make her starve drooling.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Let's go with peeling fruit, yeah...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I sliced some fruit for you. Do you want it?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Zzz...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Sleeping pretty heavy, huh.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Weird, actually, how she doesn't look all that loathsome when she's asleep.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Pinches Hibiscus's face)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Zzz...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Still running high.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hope she'll recover a little soon. That way I can prank her with a completely clean conscience.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Haaah... I've been busy half the day. I'm a little tired myself now...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Guess I can nap a little by her side...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Zzz...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Tick—tick—tick—tick—
Tick—tick—tick—tick—
Tick—tick—tick—tick—
Huh?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Tick—tick—tick—tick—
Bang.
Did that wake you up? Sorry...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: It's the alarm I set for your porridge.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Do you want it right now, or in a bit?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Now, I guess.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Lemme get it.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ah-ah-ah, don't get up. You knocked out all the way from yesterday to today and now you want to be up and about?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Lie—down—for—me.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Weagh...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (When did Hibiscus get this strong?)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I asked around a little. It was Pith who got you into this state after taking you out for special training.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: This isn't Miss Pith's fault.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: This was going to be a high-intensity training session, anyway. It might look pretty ruthless at first, but nothing ever starts smooth. I'll be fine after I'm used to it.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Still, you can't wreck yourself with training like this...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I think it's worth it. I can feel how I'm getting stronger, Originium Arts precision or otherwise, training like this.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Besides...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Besides?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I was warned about this training, going into it. It'd be majorly intense, it'd be tough making it through and I'd need a good mentality and so on.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I told the instructors: 'It's fine. My sister's a medic. Even if I end up half dead, as long as I still have breath in me, she'll bring me back.'
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: More or less how it went. You get the idea.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Lava.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: What?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I'll overlook it this time, but if you end up like this after special training again, I'll officially raise dissent with the HR department.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: You don't need to—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I don't care what kind of improvement you might get out of this. It only matters to me whether this is going to damage your health.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: No matter what, you can't...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I'm sorry...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Hibiscus? Sis?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Don't—don't cry. C'mon, look at how big you are.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Do you know how worried I was when I found you?!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I'm alright, aren't I...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Just a little overdraft on my strength. And a few grazes.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: No, not this...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Do you still remember... how you ended up at Rhodes Island...?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: That...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I helped a bunch of merchants repel some bandits, and someone noticed I was an Infected...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Then their caravan dumped me... and I remember someone or other bashed my head in. Then I passed out.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And when I woke up again, I was aboard Rhodes Island.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And somebody'd healed my injuries.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I heard an operator in the field picked me up on the way back? Lucky thing I was only minorly injured. Wasn't much trouble for others.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: They were heavy injuries...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I thought, after I lost touch with you, the next time we met, you'd still be the same awkward you, but...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Then you were on the operating table, Lava—burnt up like a fireball...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I couldn't... do anything to help...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: The only thing I could do was—attend to you after the operation... just like now.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: You were—crying my name, non-stop, in your bed...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: What? Wait, I never heard about this before...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Then—Then why didn't you tell me—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Because I knew you'd act out if you got awkward! It was so tough just finding you. What if you just ran away again?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: So before you recovered and officially came on board, I didn't even dare show up.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Ugh...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I'm not—I'm not that unreasonable.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Of course you are!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: You got lost when we left Victoria BECAUSE you were being so difficult, Lava!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: That—That was an accident...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: In any case, you can't let anything like this happen again. Do you understand?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (Quietly) Okay...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Mm-hm. There's a good girl.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Oh, that's right. What were you dreaming about?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: If you don't mind, you're safe to share some of your dreams with your sister. It'll be good for your recuperation.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Mm-hm. I'm listening.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I... I saw...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: What did you see?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I saw you...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Was there anything about me?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: You were...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Go on. I'm listening.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (Pats Lava's face)
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Hmuh?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Go on, then. What did you dream of?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (I can't, this is too embarrassing! I can't say it!)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Nothing!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Nothing at all!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Be good.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I won't!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I didn't have a single dream!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: How can you be so difficult right after waking up, Lava?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: *Sigh*...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Being difficult isn't anything new. Why is your face so red, though?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Did you manage to get a fever too?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Nope!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Just lie down now, and I'll take your temperature.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: What do you need my temperature for?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Don't bring the thermometer over, I don't have a fever! It's nothing!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: The sick aren't qualified to say it's 'nothing.'
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Can't you tell the difference between a fever and blushing?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Why would I be making you blush?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Be—Because it'd be so embarrassing having to tell you how you were so ill in my dream you couldn't even speak, duh!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Uh.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: That's more... or less how it went...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Heheh. Hearing that actually makes me pretty happy.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: It's because usually... like, sis, you're...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I'd never be taken out that easily.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Mm, but it's always hard to expect the unexpected. So in future, I really might need you to look after me, Lava.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Of course, I've always believed you'll be there to help your sister out in bad times.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Even if you usually never listen and you're always so obstinate, you have plenty of ideas, and you're always fast to act.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Is this just a really roundabout way of criticizing me...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It isn't.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: *Sigh*...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Fine.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Do you have anything to eat? I'm a little hungry.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Yep, I do.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: This is wonderful. It's not everyday we can get along so well.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Just wait a moment. I'll bring it over for you.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (So back then, she was there too, huh.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (I wondered why there was a voice that sounded so familiar.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (If not for Mr. Johann teaching me, Hibiscus wouldn't have seen me again...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (I've got no idea how he's doing these days in Leithanien. Someone as talented at music as him probably got famous by now.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Maybe a letter...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (I don't know when mum and dad'll send a reply...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Everyone's... going through really rough times...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (If I could just be more powerful, then...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Here we go, now. Here's some porridge, fresh off the flame. Eat it while it's hot.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (Sniffs it)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It doesn't really smell like anything. Isn't it meat porridge?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: In your dreams, it was. This is cutting-edge healthy porridge. Healthy AND tasty!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (Healthy?!)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: You—wait, hold on, did you put in that weird healthy powder or whatever it was you made?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: That's right. It'll be easier to absorb, and faster to deliver nutrients to your body.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Let me just ask, first... have you tasted it yourself...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Of course I have~
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I eat three square meals a day, and my nutrition's especially well-balanced. That's why it's you who gets ill and not your sister, you know.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Here, try it. Healthiness is the most important thing.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I don't wanna. I'm not gonna have a single spoonful.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I went to a lot of pains improving it. Just give it a try.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Like I'm gonna trust you! You said you improved it last time, and it still wasn't—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Here!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Wmmhphh!!!!!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Mmph?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It's like it... tastes... kind of tolerable now?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Riiight~
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Mm...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Eugh, no.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Nononono, what's up with this aftertaste?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Urp—don't tell me you just delayed the taste and called that better!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: That's right. You can drink all the porridge in one gulp now, can't you?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Hibiscus, we are NOT done!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Bleuch...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Mark my words! I am... eugh... NOT done with you!
attributes.name: Lava
